        <p>
            <h3>2. Viewing Responses</h3>
            <hr class = 'my-4'>
            From Your Woofs screen, press View Response button. It will display a new view and will display the response of the users.<br>
        </p>
        <%= image_tag 'ios_screenshots/IMG_1026.PNG', style: 'height:550px; width:auto;', class: 'img-thumbnail' %>
